requires killing the dwarf traitor in Kael Basically what I got so far is you spam a phrase, the one in the note in a certain location to make him spawn, then hand him the note that implicates him. He will then despawns and 2 giants will spawn charge into the room. Kill them and a lvl 55 giant spawns, kill this one and another lvl 55 spawns. Kill the 2nd lvl 55 giant and a lvl 60 one will spawn (boss). The level 60 one is almost 100% MR can't snare can't slow. Kill it and it will shout a line saying the giants will no longer cover for the dorf and tell him to come out as he has caused the giants lots of trouble.<br>
